<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Single specimen, ~ 30 cm long (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 43" captionStartId="F43" captionText="Figure 43. Psychropotes dyscrita (Clark, 1920). Specimen CCZ _ 083: A, B in situ images C lateral view D ventral view. Scale bars: 5 cm (A, B); 2 cm (C, D). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A, B); Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (C, D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure43" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716369" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">43A</figureCitation>
). Colouration of live specimen is yellow (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 43" captionStartId="F43" captionText="Figure 43. Psychropotes dyscrita (Clark, 1920). Specimen CCZ _ 083: A, B in situ images C lateral view D ventral view. Scale bars: 5 cm (A, B); 2 cm (C, D). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A, B); Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (C, D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure43" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716369" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">43A, B</figureCitation>
), with reddish-light purple on ventral surface (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 43" captionStartId="F43" captionText="Figure 43. Psychropotes dyscrita (Clark, 1920). Specimen CCZ _ 083: A, B in situ images C lateral view D ventral view. Scale bars: 5 cm (A, B); 2 cm (C, D). Image attribution: Durden and Smith (A, B); Wiklund, Durden, Drennan, and McQuaid (C, D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure43" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716369" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">43C</figureCitation>
). Tentacles 18, also reddish-light purple. Long, dorsal appendage with round end, slightly longer than the total body length, and developed very close to the posterior end of the body.
</paragraph>
<caption doi="10.3897/zookeys.1113.82172.figure43" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/716369" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" start="Figure 43" startId="F43">
